 class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/c89a13569997722f234f9024431d8ae6.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/c89a13569997722f234f9024431d8ae6.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/c89a13569997722f234f9024431d8ae6.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/b77a97f8db589afb4e6432c4e15f1cf2.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a broke, washed-up yoga instructor thrown out by his landlord… <br>Turn it all around with Pure Sensual Energy: <strong>the Prana Flow</strong><br>Connect with every resident in town— <br>body, mind, and something deeper— and release them one stretch at a time</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/964edc9fc912188d7414bbcee58a2f11.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=876 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/964edc9fc912188d7414bbcee58a2f11.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/964edc9fc912188d7414bbcee58a2f11.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8bf10905b185ec34648bc26a93ead2d0.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8bf10905b185ec34648bc26a93ead2d0.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8bf10905b185ec34648bc26a93ead2d0.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/464f873c052c3a9e065117033bf0fe74.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1170 height=622 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/464f873c052c3a9e065117033bf0fe74.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/464f873c052c3a9e065117033bf0fe74.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perhaps… you’ll even share your Flow with the <strong>Goddess of Yoga</strong> herself</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8e561d90bdf681c42b96bbece753633c.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8e561d90bdf681c42b96bbece753633c.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8e561d90bdf681c42b96bbece753633c.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your studio, face off against rival instructors, and make them yield… <br>or crush them completely<br>With your hands-on guidance, lead everyone toward enlightenment— <br>and <strong>experience tranquility.</strong> Abhyasa and Vairagya</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/06b3393b1f3e324e77d9c13b3a2d1081.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your yoga business, guide your students into the <strong>perfect</strong> positions with your own hands, reap your fortune, and deepen intimacy through every session. <br>In this cheerful little town, carve out your own Yoga Empire..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/b729e072ba2e6fe8f6ee875c2e85145f.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=990 height=542 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/b729e072ba2e6fe8f6ee875c2e85145f.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/b729e072ba2e6fe8f6ee875c2e85145f.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond just story and mouse clicks—our <strong>Lesson Design</strong> system throws you right into playful Intimate Sessions with your clients.<br>Drag, tap, and adjust each pose… and if things get unexpectedly steamy, just focus on your <strong>Flow</strong>. <br>Two human beings, ONE Flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/f62955159056f0df3681526a38288ceb.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=990 height=542 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/f62955159056f0df3681526a38288ceb.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/f62955159056f0df3681526a38288ceb.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/66522f87d8323b979f7497d4cdda63e6.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed by Unreal Engine, with stunning character design and lifelike performances<br><br> Expand your studio, stock up on playful tools, and unlock hidden stories— <br>revealing your clients’ deepest desires<br><br>A seamless blend of story, gameplay, intimacy, and gorgeous art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/37ed2685612e6cf2e8a2f2ac17a44b00.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1200 height=900 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/48f2bd31e7564106b46bc72f6d2d45b9.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1200 height=900 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/baa63687c1c707bf8499c739aaef70b6.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1200 height=900 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/1ba9eef9d2b6d21a8a2c32915d1b7d04.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1200 height=900 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/ac00e39718d9ed7a8079847cd7357285.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1200 height=900 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/4bd1f62e974da82924b79fc024066aff.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1200 height=900 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/c89a13569997722f234f9024431d8ae6.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/c89a13569997722f234f9024431d8ae6.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/c89a13569997722f234f9024431d8ae6.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/b77a97f8db589afb4e6432c4e15f1cf2.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a broke, washed-up yoga instructor thrown out by his landlord… <br>Turn it all around with Pure Sensual Energy: <strong>the Prana Flow</strong><br>Connect with every resident in town— <br>body, mind, and something deeper— and release them one stretch at a time</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/964edc9fc912188d7414bbcee58a2f11.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=876 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/964edc9fc912188d7414bbcee58a2f11.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/964edc9fc912188d7414bbcee58a2f11.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8bf10905b185ec34648bc26a93ead2d0.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8bf10905b185ec34648bc26a93ead2d0.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8bf10905b185ec34648bc26a93ead2d0.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/464f873c052c3a9e065117033bf0fe74.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1170 height=622 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/464f873c052c3a9e065117033bf0fe74.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/464f873c052c3a9e065117033bf0fe74.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perhaps… you’ll even share your Flow with the <strong>Goddess of Yoga</strong> herself</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8e561d90bdf681c42b96bbece753633c.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8e561d90bdf681c42b96bbece753633c.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/8e561d90bdf681c42b96bbece753633c.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your studio, face off against rival instructors, and make them yield… <br>or crush them completely<br>With your hands-on guidance, lead everyone toward enlightenment— <br>and <strong>experience tranquility.</strong> Abhyasa and Vairagya</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/06b3393b1f3e324e77d9c13b3a2d1081.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your yoga business, guide your students into the <strong>perfect</strong> positions with your own hands, reap your fortune, and deepen intimacy through every session. <br>In this cheerful little town, carve out your own Yoga Empire..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/b729e072ba2e6fe8f6ee875c2e85145f.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=990 height=542 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/b729e072ba2e6fe8f6ee875c2e85145f.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/b729e072ba2e6fe8f6ee875c2e85145f.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond just story and mouse clicks—our <strong>Lesson Design</strong> system throws you right into playful Intimate Sessions with your clients.<br>Drag, tap, and adjust each pose… and if things get unexpectedly steamy, just focus on your <strong>Flow</strong>. <br>Two human beings, ONE Flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/f62955159056f0df3681526a38288ceb.poster.avif?t=1766382986\" width=990 height=542 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/f62955159056f0df3681526a38288ceb.webm?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/f62955159056f0df3681526a38288ceb.mp4?t=1766382986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/66522f87d8323b979f7497d4cdda63e6.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed by Unreal Engine, with stunning character design and lifelike performances<br><br> Expand your studio, stock up on playful tools, and unlock hidden stories— <br>revealing your clients’ deepest desires<br><br>A seamless blend of story, gameplay, intimacy, and gorgeous art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/37ed2685612e6cf2e8a2f2ac17a44b00.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1200 height=900 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150170/extras/48f2bd31e7564106b46bc72f6d2d45b9.avif?t=1766382986\" width=1200 height=900 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src